➜这里号称“温州的小九寨”，堪称人间仙境！
http://www.sohu.com/a/169373748_390549	29299
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20170904/993dd08c888442b082094b79593088c8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20170904/62e54503cb5a42e7ab55f4b11e13c534.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>仲春树绿花艳，盛夏幽湖翠山，</p>
<p>金秋尽染山林，隆冬冰塑自然。</p>
<p>九寨沟的美，世人皆知。温州也有一个小九寨，这里森林覆盖率高达98.1%，负氧离子含量更是达到每立方厘米60000个……这里就是位于文成县的铜铃山国家森林公园。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://5b0988e595225.cdn.sohucs.com/images/20170904/07a63bfd2cf945a881c00457cac93f93.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
